(52, 'JEZ Thema Effects Demo', 'jez-jtb-effects-demo', '', '<p>Some modern web 2.0 effects is included in <strong>JEZ Thema</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul class="star"><li>Fully customizable drop-down / fly-out menu effects.</li><li>Implement switching effect for advanced search section on search component output.</li><li>More advanced effect implemented for switching OpenID login on both login module and component outputs.</li><li>Reflection effect implemented for images.</li><li>Ability to convert any link to open in modal window.</li></ul>\r\n<p class="success"><img class="fl mr1 png24" src="templates/jez_thema/images/icons/silk/arrow_left.png" border="0" /> Please follow links in the left column to see demo.</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-02-26 16:32:46', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-02-26 16:32:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 8, 'joomla themes, joomla theme, create joomla template', 'JEZ Thema Effects Demo', 0, 320, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(53, 'Navigation Effects Demo', 'navigation-effects-demo', '', '<p class="success"><img class="fl mr1 png24" src="templates/jez_thema/images/icons/silk/arrow_up.png" border="0" /> Move your mouse pointer over each menu item of the top navigation right below the logo image to see the drop-down and fly-out effects.</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-02-26 16:38:56', 62, '', '2009-06-10 04:20:45', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-02-26 16:38:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 7, 'joomla themes, joomla theme, create joomla template', 'JEZ Thema Navigation Effects Demo', 0, 762, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(54, 'Reflection.js', 'reflection-effect-info', '', '{loadmodule 53}', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-02-26 18:11:03', 62, '', '2009-02-26 18:31:31', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-02-26 18:11:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 258, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(55, 'Links Modalization', 'links-modalization', '', '<p><strong>JEZ Thema</strong> has build-in support for converting article icon links (PDF, print and email) to open in modal window. Besides this, JEZ Thema allows developers / webmasters define up to 10 custom rules to modalize any kind of link.</p>\r\n<div class="success">\r\n<p><img src="templates/jez_thema/images/icons/silk/arrow_down.png" class="fl mr1" /> Below is some sample custom rules we defined with JEZ Thema for this demo website:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="http://www.joomlaez.com/joomla-themes/create-joomla-template.html#buy-pro" class="modalWindow">a class="modalWindow"</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="http://joomlaez.com/component/mailto/?tmpl=component&link=aHR0cDovL2pvb21sYWV6LmNvbS8=">a href="http://<strong class="bold lipstick">*</strong>link=aHR0cDovL2pvb21sYWV6LmNvbS8="</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="http://www.joomlaez.com/joomla-themes/create-joomla-template.html#buy-pro" target="_modal">a target="_modal"</a>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-02-26 18:34:27', 62, '', '2009-06-10 04:36:00', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-02-26 18:34:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 5, 'joomla themes, joomla theme, create joomla template', 'JEZ Thema Modal Links Creation Demo', 0, 198, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(56, 'Sample Templates Created Based on JEZ Thema', 'sample-templates-created-based-on-jez-jtb', '', '<p>So that''s quite enought demo for introducing <strong>JEZ Thema</strong>. Below is some sample Joomla 1.5 templates created based on JEZ Thema, you can take a look at them to see how JEZ Thema do in real world.</p>  <div class="tr gr2 mb1_5">  <div class="fl tc tac">  <a href="index.php?template=jez_thema&tpl_theme=sample" title="Sample Theme depends on JEZ Thema installation" onclick="var href = location.href.replace(/(\\?|&)template=jez_(jtb|ot)(&tpl_theme=sample)?/, ''''); location.href = href + (href.indexOf(''?'') > -1 ? ''&'' : ''?'') + ''template=jez_thema&tpl_theme=sample''; return false"><img class="png24" src="images/stories/jez-jtb_sample-theme.png" border="0" alt="Sample Theme depends on JEZ Thema installation" align="center" /></a>  <br />Sample Theme depends on JEZ Thema installation  </div>  <div class="fr tac">  <a href="http://demo.joomlaez.com/create-joomla-template-with-jez-thema/sample-templates.html?template=jez_ot" title="Stand-alone Template Created Based on JEZ Thema"><img class="png24" src="images/stories/jez-ot.png" border="0" alt="Stand-alone Template Created Based on JEZ Thema" align="center" /></a>  <br />Stand-alone Template Created Based on JEZ Thema  </div>  </div>  <p class="large bold lipstick">Thank you for taking time to explore JEZ Thema demo site!</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-02-27 07:39:38', 62, '', '2009-06-11 03:12:51', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-02-27 07:39:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 13, 0, 4, 'joomla themes, joomla theme, create joomla template', 'Sample Templates Created Based on JEZ Thema', 0, 813, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(57, 'Entire Page Individual Styling', 'entire-page-individual-styling', '', '<p>With JEZ Thema, you can create individual styling for entire page, not just the component output, using Page Class Suffix defined for individual menu item.</p>\r\n<p class="success"><img border="0" src="/create-joomla-template-with-jez-thema/templates/jez_thema/images/icons/silk/arrow_left.png" class="fl mr1 png24" style="visibility: visible;"/> Please follow links in the left column to see demo.</p>\r\n<p>As you can see, all menu items in the left pointing to just same page but applying difference Page Class Suffix. For each Page Class Suffix applied, the entire page layout is changed.</p>\r\n<p>To create individual styling for each Page Class Suffix, all you need to do is prefixing CSS selector(s) with <q class="bold">body.individual-page-class-suffix&nbsp;</q>. See example below for details:</p>\r\n<pre><code>/* 2 equal width columns layout */\r\nbody.two-equal-width .gr2 #jezMain {\r\n	margin-left: 41em;\r\n	width: 39em;\r\n}\r\nbody.two-equal-width .gr2 #jezLocal {\r\n	width: 39em;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* swap position of 2 columns layout */\r\nbody.swap-position .gr2 #jezMain {\r\n	margin-left: 0;\r\n}\r\nbody.swap-position .gr2 #jezLocal {\r\n	float: right;\r\n}</code></pre>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-06-10 01:21:36', 62, '', '2009-06-10 01:59:01', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-06-10 01:21:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 310, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(58, 'Express Individual Module Styling', 'express-individual-module-styling', '', '<p>Express individual module styling is a benefit of JEZ Thema PRO edition over the free one. With express individual module styling feature, you can create individual styling for any module at any position anytime anywhere without the need of defining a module class suffix for the module requiring own style.</p>\r\n<p class="success"><img border="0" style="visibility: visible;" class="fl mr1 png24" src="/create-joomla-template-with-jez-thema/templates/jez_thema/images/icons/silk/arrow_right.png"/> See modules at the right column for express individual module styling demo.</p>\r\n<p>When using JEZ Thema''s advanced module chromes, each module will be automatically applied an additional class generated from its title by lowercasing all alphanumeric characters then stripping out all non-alphanumeric characters with white space character replaced with <span class="bold">-</span> character.</p>\r\n<p>For example, if the module title is <span class="bold">Act Now! Only Few Days Left</span> then the additional auto-generated class attribute for that module will be <span class="bold">act-now-only-few-days-left</span>. If the module is rendered using JEZ Thema''s <span class="bold">jezRounded1Img</span> then creating individual style for it is as simple as defining style for following CSS selectors:</p>\r\n<pre><code>.jezRounded1Img.act-now-only-few-days-left .inner,\r\n.jezRounded1Img.act-now-only-few-days-left .t,\r\n.jezRounded1Img.act-now-only-few-days-left .b,\r\n.jezRounded1Img.act-now-only-few-days-left .b div {\r\n	/* put individual rounded corner background image here */\r\n}\r\n.jezRounded1Img.act-now-only-few-days-left h3 {\r\n	/* put individual style for module here */\r\n}</code></pre>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-06-10 02:11:14', 62, '', '2009-06-10 08:56:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-06-10 02:11:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 237, 'robots=\nauthor=');
